Debt Crisis Threatens Financial System, Finland’s Tuominen Says

-- B y   K a t i   P o h j a n p a l o
-- 
2011-10-14T08:37:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-14/debt-crisis-threatens-financial-system-finland-s-tuominen-says.html
The European sovereign debt crisis
threatens the region’s financial system and real economy, Anneli
Tuominen, Director General at  Finland ’s Financial Supervisory
Authority said in a hearing in the Helsinki-based parliament
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
